    public abstract class AbstractPipeliningResponseListener
extends ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener<SMTPResponse>
    ChainedSMTPClientFutureListener implementation which should get sub-classed by implementations which may be used within the PIPELINING context. It makes sure the callbacks will not get executed if SMTPClientFutureImpl
